data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Summerfield Community of Riverview, Florida. This spacious and beautifully designed residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an impressive 2,011 square feet of living space, offering ample room for your family's comfort and enjoyment.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the inviting ambiance created by the new laminate wood floors that stretch throughout the entire home. The ceramic tile in all wet areas ensures easy maintenance and adds a touch of sophistication to the property.    Entertaining is a breeze with both a family room and a separate living room, providing plenty of space for gatherings with friends and loved ones. Whether you're hosting a movie night or just a cozy evening alone, this home caters to your every need.    The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring modern appliances, abundant cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar for quick meals on busy mornings. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the dining area and family room, promoting a warm and inclusive atmosphere.    At the end of the day, retreat to the tranquil master bedroom with its own ensuite bath, complete with a relaxing bathtub and a walk-in shower. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, perfect for accommodating guests, a home office, or your hobbies.    One of the standout features of this property is the expansive 3-car garage, providing ample storage for vehicles, tools, and recreational equipment. Whether you have multiple cars or simply enjoy the extra space for storage, this garage has you covered.    Nestled within the sought-after Summerfield Community, residents here enjoy a host of amenities, including a community pool, clubhouse, playgrounds, and golf. The neighborhood's convenient location provides easy access to local schools, shopping centers, dining options, and major roadways for an effortless commute to Tampa and beyond.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent house your new home. Schedule a private tour today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in the heart of Riverview's Summerfield Community!
